content: In 1996, Garry Kasparov played a 6-game match against Deep Blue, IBM's supercomputer, and won 4 x 2.
translations: ita:Nel 1996, Garry Kasparov ha giocato un incontro da 6 partite contro Deep Blue, il supercomputer di IBM, e ha vinto 4 x 2
credits: Sentence from Tatoeba by carlosalberto (CC-BY 2.0 FR)
